                    </div>
                    <span>I didn't find this reference any good UNTIL I knew vi well. It is OK for a quick look up to remember a command; but to learn something new or more than you already know forget it. I have a coffee mug with vi commands on it that is far more helpful. Because of this experience, I am reluctant to buy others in this series (e.g. Python Pocket Reference).</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Nice little pocket review</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
